data.description: Gorgeous downtown condo looks brand new & is move-in ready! Barely lived in vacation home is loaded with energy efficient features - solar panels, tankless water heater, spray foam insulation & more! Tons of storage with multiple closets for bikes & toys. Quartz counters, stainless appliances & gas cooking. Flex Rm is perfect for office & pantry space. Perfect lock & leave lifestyle for the urban dweller - walk to the Riverwalk, Blue Star Brewery & all that Southtown has to offer! Small yard for pets too! Vacant and safe to show!
data.whatILove: We bought this home because it is the perfect getaway from our hectic lives!  The fact that it is a lock and leave home that we don't have to worry about when we are not there really helps with the enjoyment of the place.  The yard and everything is taken care of even when we are not there.  There is so much to enjoy about downtown San Antonio and Southtown has so much to offer.  You can very easily get on your bike and be where everything is happening in just minutes or take a stroll and enjoy restaurants, art, bars, the Riverwalk and more within minutes.
